query:
SELECT 
  ps.id,
  p.name as produto,
  ps.supplierName,
  ps.supplierCode,
  ps.costPrice / 100.0 as preco_custo,
  ps.purchasePrice / 100.0 as preco_compra,
  ps.isDefault
FROM product_suppliers ps
JOIN products p ON ps.productId = p.id
LIMIT 10;
